overview.en: Authpaper Delivery uses blockchain to provide a peer-to-peer platform to deliver confidential data with unforgeable delivery records. Authpaper Delivery is also a platform for users to issue unforgeable certifications.
overview.zh: Authpaper Delivery 利用區塊鏈建立一套P2P私密資料傳送平台, 資料只有寄件收件方能閱讀, 而傳送記錄公開又不能被偽造. 這平台也容許組織發出不能偽造的證書.
